    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 裁员 400 人，裁员规模开始显现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/northvolt-jobs-losses-begin-to-crystallize-with-400-staff-let-go</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的瑞典电池制造商 Northvolt AB 在与瑞典两家工会达成的谈判结束后，已在其位于谢莱夫特奥的运营中心解雇了近 400 名白领工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/northvolt-jobs-losses-begin-to-crystallize-with-400-staff-let-go</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 12:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
